ant contribution at $\\sim0.2$ MeV due to E2/M1 radiation enhanced by the\n$5/2^-$ resonance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 18:49:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2021 20:11:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
